title: Ennavo Ennavo Lyrics Priyamanavale
stanzas:
Ennavo ennavo
en vasam naanillai
enna naan solvadho
ennidam vaarthai illai

Ennavo ennavo
en vasam naanillai
enna naan solvadho
ennidam vaarthai illai

mazhai thaedi naan nenaiven
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa
kudaiyaaga naan varuven
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa

viral pidithu nagam kadippen
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa
nee kadikka naan valarppen
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa

vidikaalai velai varai
en vasam nee sammadhamaa.
idaivelai vendumendru
idai kaetkum sammadhamaa

nee paadhi naan paadhi
endrirukka sammadhamaa
ennuyiril saripaadhi
naan tharuven sammadhamaa

Ennavo ennavo
en vasam naanillai
enna naan solvadho
ennidam vaarthai illai

imaiyaaga naan iruppen
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa
imaikkaamal paarthiruppen
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa

kanavaaga naan varuven
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa
kanmoodi thavam iruppen
sammadhamaa sammadhamaa

oru kodi raathirigal
madi thoonga sammadhamaa
pala kodi pournamigal
paarthidave sammadhamaa

priyaatha varam ondrai
tharavendum sammadhamaa
printhaalai unnai serum
uyir vendum sammadhamaa

Ennavo ennavo
en vasam naanillai
enna naan solvadho
ennidam vaarthai illai
